myTk.py contains the class myTk which is a layer between the
application code and the tkinter class. This is similar to
a previous written Perl class.

dirgrep.py is a program that uses myTk. It's purpose is to search
a files in a specified directory for a string. The file containing
the string can be opened by double clicking on the line in the
result window.

think.py is a program used to test out simple concepts before
adding them to myTk.py and/or dirgrep.py

